title: Understanding Cumulative Relative Frequency
text: Cumulative relative frequency is the sum of the relative frequencies for all classes up to and including the current class.

title: Identify the Relevant Range
text: Look for the cumulative relative frequency corresponding to heights less than $$65.95$$ inches.
